cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR 

This paper deals with video-based person re-identification, which is a problem in computer vision. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which are commonly used in the sub-categories of cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves attention mechanisms, which are a popular topic in the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
